Dear all,

meanwhile I have tested the following procedure to get Rmpi to work on a 
multicore Debian squeeze box with a kernel from backports.org:

I installed the squeeze version of the package r-cran-rmpi. This does not load 
because of the missing namespace. But it pulls in all dependencies needed at 
runtime.

I then installed the build dependencies by apt-get build-dep.

Within R, I then used install.packages() to install Rmpi. This installed the 
package and it loaded fine.

Kind regards,

Johannes

